Quickstrike:





He made his decision. Revenge would be made. The pressure in his head 
turned him insane to a point. But still, he was smart enough to act 
right around the ones he trusted, even how small allies were.

In the open, Quickstrike opened his comm-link to Blackarachnia's. He 
let the open trasmittion linger, just in case she wasn't alone. Then 
after a minute, he said, "Blackarachnia. Ah need t' talk t' ya. 
Follow mah signature; ah ain't too far, jus' two klicks away. Come 
alone."
